body.name: Aenllosi Hard Case Replacement for GL.iNet GL-SFT1200 / GL-MT1300 / GL-A1300 Secure Travel WiFi Router
deliveryMessages: FREE delivery Tuesday, February 20 on orders shipped by Amazon over $35. Order within 13 hrs 18 mins
features: This case is specially designed for GL mt1300 travel router, this case is sturdy, shockproof and waterproof to protect your beloved mt1300 router. The GL mt1300 beryl case can hold your GL.iNet gl mt1300 well and effectively cushion the shock caused by accidental drop, keeping your device in good condition.

You can take your GL iNet sft1200 to travel at any time with confidence, it can be easily put into your backpack, suitcase, or placed anywhere, and you never have to worry about your GL.iNet sft1200 being damaged. For a perfect fit, the classic zipper design makes it easy to open and close.

The hard case is suitable as a replacement for the GL sft1200 opal, the interior is made of high-quality velvet, and the soft inner structure ensures the protection of the GLiNet sft1200. This opal travel router case comes with a comfortable hand strap for easy access when traveling or for storage, and the inner mesh pocket not only secures your GL.iNet opal case but also stores your accessories.

The hard case is small but strong enough to keep your GL iNet beryl travel router safe and convenient. This portable GLiNet beryl router case protects your GL i.Net beryl in all kinds of harsh conditions.
Note: Only the case is sold, GL.iNet GL-SFT1200 / GL-MT1300 / GL-A1300 Secure Travel WiFi Router and accessories are not included.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Correctly sized, nice case
reviews.reviewText: I've been looking for a model-specific case for my travel router for well over a year now, and this Aenllosi hard case is correctly sized for the perfect fit for the model I have. Makes it far easier to pack and keeps the power supply cord from getting tangled or caught in other things in my bag. Love it!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect fit for the GL.iNet GL-SFT1200
reviews.reviewText: This carrying case has solid sides for a little extra protection and fits the GL-SFT1200 perfectly as well as the power cable. It's a little thicker than the original box, but smaller in all other dimensions. I'm not sure volume wise if it will take It should take up less space in my suitcase for when I travel. It seems solidly built and should last significantly longer than the original cardboard box. I'm very pleased!
